body_html:
This is because since the version string was updated from 0.10.0rc0 to 0.10.0, there hasn't been a passing build in the Linux GPU nightly configuration yet. See history: http://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Nightly/job/nightly-matrix-linux-gpu/

To work around this temporarily, use URLs in which 0.10.0 is replaced with 0.10.0rc0. It should resolve itself when they pass.
Sorry about the inconvenience.
